mcp.placeholder_server_config:
Paste or enter MCP server configuration. Batch add is supported.

Example:
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "playwright": {
      "command": "npx",
      "args": ["@playwright/mcp@latest"]
    }
  }
}

mcp.placeholder_edit_server_config:
Edit server configuration. Smart batch add is supported.

Example:
{
  "command": "npx",
  "args": ["@playwright/mcp@latest"],
  "env": {}
}
